Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirisaki-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.17,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.88,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your favorite soccer team won, didn't they?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you watched last night's game!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right! That makes three games in a row!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess you could chalk it up to the "Friend Notebook."
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.31,0:00:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since that day,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirisaki has been slowly warming up to the class.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.11,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, she wasn't the shy type to begin with,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.90,0:00:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so maybe she just needed a little help getting back into her natural state.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.95,0:01:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, life is good!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}this{\i0} is the high school life that I dreamed of!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even plants and animals sound like a blast to me now!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.40,0:01:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.97,0:01:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to this!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.26,0:01:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls and I made plans to go to McDonald's after school!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.37,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous or what?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? I go there a lot too, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.11,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if only I could break up with this little bean sprout, my life would be perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.25,0:01:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at 'cha, Princess Gorilla.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.01,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the longest time, she would only give me hostile looks,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.06,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but these days, I think I'm beginning to see her smile more often.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.34,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at, you super-pervert? You're creeping me out!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nope, she hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! We're going to get this done ASAP!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you help out, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are seriously sewn at the hip. I have to hand it to them.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good for them.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally hooked on each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.59,0:02:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that good? Where does that leave you?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.58,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a crush on Ichijou-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How long... How long have you...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think I couldn't tell? I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.99,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Ichijou-kun has a girlfriend, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd only come between them!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was convinced this whole time that Ichijou-kun had a thing for you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! He can't possibly have a crush on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.92,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? From where I stand, it's painfully obvious.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I wished you two would get together already and get it over with.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty irritating, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you would hold back a little, Ruri-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.18,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, nobody said you're not allowed to go after a boy
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.41,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,just because he's already in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be that as it may...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Kosaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set up an opportunity for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait! Wait a second, Ruri-chan! What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.58,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to hold a study group in your bedroom today. How about it?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.33,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
