Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I do. Can you bring us some tea?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did I land myself in this mess?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.65,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have the slightest clue why Miyamoto would suddenly suggest a study group at my place,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that's not the issue at hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera's coming over! Am I allowed to be this blessed?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you tagging along, Maiko-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, where's the harm?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're eyeglasses buddies, see?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you pair us like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me it was actually Onodera's idea,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she just got Miyamoto to ask in her place?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Did she just look away? B-But why?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really! Thanks a lot, Ruri-chan for putting strange ideas in my head!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? I can't look him in the face!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's... It's going to be okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down, Raku! Remember, your house is the headquarters of a yakuza clan, the Shuei-gumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she's just super nervous!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So jittery...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.82,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart won't stop... So jittery...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.64,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What's got you worked up? Why're you so jittery?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What... I'm not jittery, or excited, or anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you were excited, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't help it, can I?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to a study group with my friends before.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a bad thing for me to get excited?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So this is your room, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.89,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I haven't been in here in ages, either. Everything's still the same, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this room is tiny! And it kind of smells funny.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.71,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could she say that in front of Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It smells like Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.46,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looked away again!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! I did it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, your tea is ready!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ryu!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Are you all right, Young Master?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Are you all right, Onodera?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.48,0:06:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good... I'm so on edge I have no clue what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just cool your head, and focus on your work!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.61,0:06:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruri-chan, can you solve this one?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.53,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichijou-kun! I'd appreciate it if you showed Kosaki how to do this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,R-R-Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.78,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! It's way beyond me.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you solved one that looked even harder the other day!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, just go! And don't you dare come back!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please show me how to do this problem!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.38,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa! Can you believe this development? \NOnodera and I are so close!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you solve it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think so...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, crap! My heart's pounding so hard that math is the last thing on my mind!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound of my heartbeat is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet even Onodera can hear it!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, the fact is she's asking me for help.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I gotta play it cool, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? Hey, this is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to substitute the variable {\i1}a{\i0} first, or else it's unsolvable.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.79,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your deal? Worry about your own homework.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already done.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.42,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She assigned us three worksheets for homework—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}U-Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.46,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And here I thought that I had the upper hand in schoolwork!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What were your grades like in the US, Kirisaki-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly A's, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onodera, I'm pretty good with schoolwork. Want me to help?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You just take this, and do this...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's amazing! I got it! Your explanation makes so much sense!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirisaki, you'll pay for this...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... By the way, Onodera-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a crush on anybody?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a question you just suddenly ask a person?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly? Look, it's freaking girl talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that a weird question?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right now, I don't think of anyone like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I don't think of anyone like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.94,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see! I see... So Onodera isn't into anyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good job, Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I don't have anyone like that now, either!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope I can meet that special someone soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just so hard, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Joking, I'm joking! That was a joke!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, that was mean, honey.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say those things when you've got me!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.03,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So sorry, darling! I just wanted to tease you a little.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jeez, what am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay! You two sure are chummy!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Kirisaki-san—can I ask you something, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.11,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Spill the beans... How far have you two gone?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How? How? How? How far?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How far have we gone—what exactly do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, you know, ki—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Come with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Raku? You gave me a shock!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me! Now's as good a time as ever, so I'm gonna tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen up!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.01,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you dare tell anyone else either!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.83,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. So that's why you've been pretending to be a couple.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.52,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? So you were onto us? You knew we were pretending to be a couple?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.30,0:09:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hey, it was pretty obvious from my end.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be perfectly honest...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku, I couldn't be more jealous!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you get a girlfriend before me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was about when I figured it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was right at the beginning!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, you humiliated me knowing full well that we were pretending?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you really think I could've resisted the urge?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why I didn't want to tell him!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.91,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'd rather not have Onodera actually fall for your act the whole three years, if at all possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.31,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, hey, it couldn't be any simpler. Just tell her how you feel!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I could do something like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.31,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I happen to think the odds are in your favor.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.32,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Onodera has a crush on you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... No way...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, come on, there's no way she'd...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your sweet time.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.34,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if it's really true that Onodera has a thing for me...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a lot done, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we sure did!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How perfect would that make my life?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.78,0:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Young Master and the Mistress haven't gotten
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,very far in their relationship, eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.75,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally brings her home, but with a whole bunch of other friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.41,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's time for us to give them a little nudge. Whaddya say?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.30,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what's the big idea, randomly calling us out here?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was enjoying myself, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, apparently there's some expensive tea in the storehouse out back
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and they want us to come get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I guess it was good timing.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, I was so self-conscious with Onodera around.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just being in the same room made it hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the storehouse they were talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. They said we can't miss it once we're inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Come on in.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurry up and get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? You could at least give me a—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really can't figure you out...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go for it, Young Master.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is as far as we can take you!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Damn it...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing? Open the door!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They got us. This is why they called us.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.87,0:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I'll bet they're like, "This is as far as we can take you!"
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, but still. There's a window and a ladder,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so it's not like we couldn't get out if we put our minds to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kirisaki?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! Thanks to my guys, we're stuck.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.19,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've been unusually quiet for the last few minutes...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.10,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kirisaki-san?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up! Just be quiet for a minute!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you look at me, I'll smash your face in, got it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.07,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Geh!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'd smash your face in if you looked at me, didn't I?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't catch a break!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been afraid of dark, cramped spaces since I was little. Like this storehouse.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.18,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago I got stuck inside a washing machine and couldn't move for five hours.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How exactly did that happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not clinging to you because I want to!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all I can do to keep myself calm.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get the point, then just shut up and let me keep clinging!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.38,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell? She's totally different from her usual self!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who knew that she had this side to her?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.62,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking at her now,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realize that she's just like any other girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until this moment, I'd never really thought of her as one, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa, talk about in-my-face!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.93,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I gonna do? I can hear the whisper of her breath!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her eyes... are glistening with tears.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.75,0:14:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, her eyes are so big, they're adorable. And check out those eyelashes!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.41,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's the scent of a shampoo I've never smelled before as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, I can feel her warmth on my back!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.73,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her lips are sparkling... and they look so soft... for some reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.92,0:14:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I've ignored her till now, but this girl's pretty hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what the hell am I thinking?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I've already got... When I've already decided who to give my heart to—Onodera!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, being alone with a girl in this situation in a locked room like this
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is already questionable in more ways than one...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, see that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A ladder!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use that to get out through the window up there?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, we could probably get out that way,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you in any shape to climb?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess not.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.03,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least if you got out first, and went to get somebody.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.13,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I could leave behind someone who's in as sorry shape as you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.86,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing I need is for you to start sobbing on me afterwards.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just give it some time, they'll come back for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.93,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm keeping you company, so don't give me that bravado!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.20,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you playing the cool guy now?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You playing Mr. Cool isn't going to get us very...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hey, {\i1}excuse me{\i0} for trying...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.16,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then, keep talking to me. I'm fine with anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go quiet again, I'll start to get scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What am I supposed to...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.30,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like some awesome story, or...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're really putting me on the spot, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just suddenly pull something out of thin air.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.53,0:16:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Okay, then... How do you feel about Onodera-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.39,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How? How do I...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a really great person, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute, and so sweet.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.35,0:16:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that she and I could be great friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I admit Onodera's pretty great.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's both caring and affable.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's hot, and well-groomed, and adorable, and feminine,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's got a beautiful smile...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's absolutely the ideal girl, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.24,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do you think Onodera-san's...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, crap! I gushed too hard!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree! She gives of this totally feminine aura!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what I'm saying, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank God she's so dense!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, a while ago Shu asked me something.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.98,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone so hung up about whether you've ever been kissed or not?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that stuff?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.32,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, being somewhat interested myself—I can understand, but still...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't look at me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the one thing I do know for sure
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I'd rather die than have to kiss you!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Right back at you!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you've ever kissed someone!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? Are you saying you have?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And for your information, I've kissed tons of people!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And overseas, kissing is our way of saying hello, so there!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about kissing on the lips, not your goddamn cheeks!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! What's so special about a smack on the lips?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss is a kiss!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between a romantic kiss and a friendly one is difference between day and night!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up, like you've ever done it before, either!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than acting like a kiss on the cheek counts!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You'll never kiss anyone as long as you live, anyway!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to talk, you gorilla girl!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.64,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'm not that freaked out anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm okay to climb the ladder now.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! In that case, let's get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.86,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look out!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Move...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You first.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you safe, Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking so long to come home that I contacted the yakuza, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.98,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk... You two may be boyfriend and girlfriend...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's too soon for such antics?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This isn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ichijou-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.09,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are! Thank goodness, I was worried—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Onodera?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.29,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry for barging in!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, this adventure-filled study group...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Young Miss?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a huge misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.50,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}came to a close, as I somehow lost many things that were important to me.
