Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just the two of us now, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Ruri-chan, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.18,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you like, ever been kissed, Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at your face!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in no way obligated to answer that.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, when did I give you permission to address me casually?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, where's the harm? We're glasses buddies!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. You're Ichijou-kun's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's strange?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Him and Kirisaki-san, that's what!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.88,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't feel like they're actually dating.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.59,0:20:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such things! It's cruel to a couple pursuing pure love!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.14,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad that I have to doubt Kirisaki-san, but I'm a little suspicious of those two.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you know something about it...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kirisaki-san? What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so gonna rip this guy a new one.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.95,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You've been deceived!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right of the stairs.
